NO MATTER HOW LONG YOU PLAN TO STAY
YOU'LL SEE MORE OF MEXICO BY CMA «
... . . . . . . . . . ...•
"Mexico is so big--and our time is limited!"
That's the lament of many travelers, but don't
let it worry you ... because CMA, Mexico's
leading airline, offers you deluxe daily flights
between Mexico City and all the other im-
portant cities. So, whether your time be limit-
ed or ample, make Mexico City your head-
quarters and let CMA fly you to the most
distant centers of attraction -- you'll see more
places and have more time to see them,
because you save valuable days otherwise
wasted in surface travel.
Mexico is not only a lush vacationland. It's a
place where your dollar buys a lot more, too.
Travel by CMA is relatively inexpensive, as
are hotel accommodations and meals. At low
cost the whole panorama of Mexico is yours
to explore. You reach Mexico City quickly,
too. CMA's DC-4s make it a non-stop over-
night hop from Los Angeles. Or you can
cross the Border and fly more leisurely from
Tijuana or Mexicali, stopping at Hermosillo,
Mazatlan, and Guadalajara en route. However
you go you'll enjoy a smooth trip, because
CMA's route is mostly over level ground.
CMA service is first-class in every respect,
equal to the finest offered in the
U.S. A. See your travel agent or the
nearest Pan American ticket office for fares
and schedules.
